Random Potion: 
---------------
Title: Elixir
Effect: Animal form. Makes the user turn into a random animal.
Strength: Regular with a slight side effect.
Side Effect: Bad luck.
Container: A translucent beer bottle.
Colour: Purple.
Appearance: Translucency.
Texture: Oily.
Taste: Magically the most desirable thing to you.
Label: A warning of an ancient curse.
Duration: 30 minutes
Curability: Novice Level (Easiest)
---------------
